  Source:
    Title: Harijan
    Editor: Mohandas Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 6 March 1937
---
There are subjects where reason cannot take us far and we have to accept
things on faith, Faith then does not contradict reason but transcends it,
Faith is a kind of sixth sense which works in cases which are without the
purview of reason.
